patchomv (1.3.0-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * more descriptive naming of timer and service unit files and scripts by using the command names of tasks
  * more descriptive naming of timer and service unit files and rsync scripts by using the names of source shared folders
  * use symlinks to renamed scripts because the GUI depends on filenames with job.uuid
  * omv 8.2.7 finally uses %h for avahi service names, so no need to set them and therefor unset them
  * depend on omv >= 8.2.7

 -- Simone Karin Lehmann <skl@lisanet.de>  Sun, 19 Apr 2026 15:36:09 +0200

